WEBVTT

00:57.445 --> 01:04.212
Today, I don’t mind to tell you about what’s
happening

01:05.296 --> 01:12.752
in the other lokas, which we don’t see,
of which we are not aware.

01:16.204 --> 01:20.550
It may frighten you a little bit. But
the time has come for us to know,

01:22.576 --> 01:26.055
how are we placed in relation to the whole?

01:28.177 --> 01:36.079
What are the plans of the Divine? And how
are we going to fulfil them?

01:40.845 --> 01:44.802
Now most of you are here Realized souls.

01:44.802 --> 01:49.601
Some of you have come first time; you will
also get your Realization.

01:50.734 --> 01:54.095
But the common point is that you are all
seekers -

01:54.096 --> 02:00.910
seekers of God, seekers of peace, seekers
of love. That’s a common point.

02:02.644 --> 02:11.386
But this seeking has come to you not
for your own sake,

02:12.117 --> 02:14.867
for an individual ascent

02:15.165 --> 02:22.087
or for some achievements of a place from
where there is no return,

02:24.365 --> 02:30.220
but this is the last judgment that all
the human beings have to face.

02:32.705 --> 02:36.980
They have to go through it and to achieve
their last,

02:38.843 --> 02:43.438
achieve their places in the kingdom of God.

02:44.007 --> 02:49.676
Today you are sitting before Me; you have
been with Me before and much before.

02:49.936 --> 02:55.371
But today especially when you are with Me,

02:55.572 --> 03:00.073
you have come here to face up to it and to see for yourself

03:00.274 --> 03:03.307
that you are able to bear the truth,

03:03.308 --> 03:05.629
the love, the blessings of God.

03:05.786 --> 03:11.896
That you can enter into the Kingdom of God and abide there

03:12.414 --> 03:17.916
in his reign with all his powers flowing through you.

03:18.692 --> 03:22.889
It has been promised before. All promises are to be fulfilled.

03:22.889 --> 03:30.111
All scriptures are to be supported and are to be proved.

03:33.967 --> 03:42.164
But we must know that there is a great war going on

03:42.164 --> 03:45.809
between satanic forces and Divine forces

03:46.890 --> 03:53.452
and all the satanic forces who symbolized as

03:54.047 --> 03:59.771
devils – in Sanskrit language they are called as rakshasas, asuras and all that,

04:00.179 --> 04:05.015
have taken their birth on this Earth

04:06.051 --> 04:13.164
to demolish the kingdom of God. Imagine, what ambitions!

04:13.578 --> 04:18.051
But they want to demolish this kingdom of God in your hearts.

04:18.361 --> 04:22.842
The kingdom of God exists, will exist, it’s eternal.

04:23.342 --> 04:26.792
It has created Universes after Universes.

04:26.792 --> 04:29.845
it has created human beings from amoeba to this stage.

04:29.846 --> 04:37.789
It has brought you to this position that today you are here to receive your ultimate goal.

04:41.769 --> 04:45.095
It all has happened now.

04:45.095 --> 04:48.015
At this critical moment,

04:49.935 --> 04:55.398
at this precious moment, when you are about to enter into the kingdom of God,

04:55.398 --> 04:59.850
all these forces are built up to pull you down.

05:02.569 --> 05:05.374
It lies in your wisdom to understand

05:05.374 --> 05:10.164
that the forces are very subtle, extremely cunning

05:10.164 --> 05:12.164
beyond your comprehension.

05:15.276 --> 05:19.938
Even after entering into Self-realized state,

05:19.938 --> 05:21.938
you have noticed, how they act on you,

05:22.371 --> 05:25.887
try to drag you down, pull you down.

05:29.136 --> 05:35.530
This war is played not on the conscious plane as it was played before.

05:36.047 --> 05:38.410
Say one rakshasa coming in was all right to kill him,

05:38.410 --> 05:41.319
he came as a rakshasa, he came as a devil, he was killed, finished.

05:42.406 --> 05:45.365
But today they have come as Godly men,

05:45.365 --> 05:48.834
as God men as they call them, as God women.

05:49.035 --> 05:51.746
They call themselves as gods, gurus.

05:51.746 --> 05:54.169
They have come in the garb of religion.

05:56.524 --> 05:59.513
These ancient rakshasas have taken their births

06:01.402 --> 06:04.852
and they have gone into the minds of the seekers.

06:05.416 --> 06:08.452
Thousands and thousands of seekers they
have captured!

06:08.452 --> 06:13.021
Imagine the situation is so, so precarious and so dangerous.

06:14.593 --> 06:18.552
They have entered into the minds of the people who are the seekers,

06:18.738 --> 06:21.999
who are the ones who are to be bestowed with this kingdom,

06:21.999 --> 06:26.874
who are to be enthroned,

06:26.874 --> 06:30.030
who are to be crowned,

06:31.947 --> 06:41.435
have been destroyed, tortured by these horrible forces.

06:45.716 --> 06:49.748
And because it is not in your conscious plane, you cannot see them,

06:49.748 --> 06:52.550
you cannot feel them, you cannot understand
them.

06:52.803 --> 06:54.848
How dangerous they are!

06:54.848 --> 07:00.083
While they have learnt all the methods of coming into your ego or into your superego

07:00.083 --> 07:03.054
to influence you.

07:06.098 --> 07:09.566
That war we all have to fight.

07:11.507 --> 07:15.577
If we have to establish ourselves fully in the kingdom of God,

07:15.577 --> 07:22.111
you must know that we have to fight all those pulling forces.

07:24.340 --> 07:27.810
Sahaja Yoga is not meant for useless people,

07:27.810 --> 07:30.799
it's not meant for people who have no courage.

07:30.799 --> 07:33.778
It's not meant for cowards.

07:33.967 --> 07:38.249
It’s not meant for people who run after money and who run after all these material things.

07:38.489 --> 07:43.819
Especially the first people who are the foundation of Sahaja Yoga.

07:44.181 --> 07:52.408
They have to be people of great caliber and
of great desire to achieve

07:52.853 --> 07:59.703
their state of emancipation

08:01.238 --> 08:07.604
because they are the people who are going to save the whole humanity.

08:07.759 --> 08:10.477
They are the redeemers.

08:10.478 --> 08:17.654
They are the ones who are going to manifest the salvation of this doomed humanity.

08:17.810 --> 08:26.005
Those who are weak can be strengthened because the energy lies within them.

08:27.211 --> 08:30.218
Those who are unhealthy can be cured.

08:30.477 --> 08:33.280
Those who are mentally disturbed can be brought round.

08:33.280 --> 08:38.665
But there is no place for cowards in this.

08:38.795 --> 08:43.214
You have to be courageous and cheerful people.

08:43.389 --> 08:51.691
For one thing because you represent that force which is fighting for the Divine,

08:51.691 --> 08:56.336
for God Almighty. You are his hands.

08:56.670 --> 08:59.862
And you have to be wise also.

08:59.862 --> 09:04.838
Stupid people are no good.

09:06.447 --> 09:11.606
Stupidity can never help you to rise.

09:11.606 --> 09:16.220
You have to be wise people.

09:17.507 --> 09:22.784
Useless people, those who run after nonsensical things,

09:22.784 --> 09:25.311
let them go wherever they like.

09:25.311 --> 09:26.968
They’ll come back

09:26.968 --> 09:31.257
when their time and turn will come.

09:31.257 --> 09:38.330
We need not be many people for this.

09:38.486 --> 09:47.142
Very few can save the world but they have to be strong

09:47.408 --> 09:54.957
and absolutely established in their understanding of the Powers of their Spirit

09:55.086 --> 10:01.592
powers of their Father who is Almighty.

10:02.161 --> 10:06.791
Don’t worry what happened to you before getting your Realization.

10:07.103 --> 10:12.551
Those who ponder over these things will not achieve much.

10:12.551 --> 10:16.215
Past is past, is finished. Now today you are facing Me and I am facing you.

10:16.365 --> 10:22.645
This is the present.

10:23.858 --> 10:30.989
It is not possible for Me to give you the complete vision of the great war that is on

10:30.990 --> 10:35.836
and how you are to be saved.

10:36.240 --> 10:43.708
The tempest, I feel, in a boat, I have put in my children in.

10:43.889 --> 10:49.022
Try to keep in the center to keep the gravity all right.

10:49.281 --> 10:52.560
And when you’ll get strong enough,

10:52.561 --> 10:56.813
you will row the boat with Me.

10:57.349 --> 11:00.536
Do not hate yourself.

11:00.537 --> 11:04.739
Do not torture yourself and don’t feel guilty by which you become very, very weak.

11:04.739 --> 11:08.111
What is there to feel guilty? I don’t understand.

11:08.260 --> 11:14.167
Imagine a warrior and a soldier feeling guilty at the time when the war is on.

11:14.167 --> 11:21.381
You have to be full of enthusiasm and full of valor.

11:21.692 --> 11:26.610
All these small, petty things, which destroy your Spirit,

11:26.610 --> 11:29.172
throw them away.

11:29.172 --> 11:33.338
No place for all these fashionable things of feeling guilty.

11:33.493 --> 11:39.566
This is the weakness of the West.

11:40.186 --> 11:44.962
If you have to progress fast and if you want all this to be achieved,

11:45.143 --> 11:47.285
time is very short.

11:47.533 --> 11:51.692
You have to realize there is no time for hanky-pankies as you call it.

11:51.967 --> 11:56.337
But there is no time also for going round the places.

11:56.492 --> 12:00.132
You have to settle down now.

12:00.132 --> 12:02.455
You have to get to it.

12:02.455 --> 12:05.604
So many Realized souls are born today as children

12:05.604 --> 12:09.579
in all the communities even in Russia, can you imagine?

12:09.863 --> 12:12.945
Russians are going to come to Sahaja Yoga.

12:12.945 --> 12:17.450
I have been there. They may be the first

12:17.908 --> 12:21.478
because they have reasoned out all the nonsense of the so-called religious

12:21.478 --> 12:29.599
and the religiosities and all the nonsense
of the false people who preach religion.

12:30.013 --> 12:33.643
There is no place for false gurus in Russia, no place.

12:33.643 --> 12:37.646
Also for real gurus there is no place.

12:38.215 --> 12:42.222
So you have to get, enter there through their children

12:42.377 --> 12:47.594
and children will recognize Sahaja Yoga.

12:47.595 --> 12:53.571
Within ten years’ time everything has to spark.

12:54.518 --> 13:01.791
It does not matter how you do it but you have to do it.

13:01.953 --> 13:07.358
For Me and for the Divine, you are the most important things.

13:07.530 --> 13:17.866
Doesn’t matter if there is an earthquake and few horrible buildings fall down.

13:18.750 --> 13:21.992
It makes no difference to the Divine.

13:21.992 --> 13:27.784
What is important is how many are aware? How many are progressing?

13:27.967 --> 13:32.674
How many are settling down?

13:32.984 --> 13:39.136
Those who are very frightened type have no place in Sahaja Yoga.

13:39.706 --> 13:45.219
That means you are still playing into the hands of these negative forces.

13:45.815 --> 13:49.815
Imagine frightened people coming as soldiers for Sahaja Yoga?

13:50.530 --> 13:52.553
I mean...

13:55.066 --> 14:00.547
All the powers that are within you will start manifesting when you show your valor.

14:00.547 --> 14:11.351
When you are not even willing to raise your hand, how your sword is going to work?

14:12.580 --> 14:17.353
In India, now there are thousands and thousands of Sahaja Yogis.

14:17.522 --> 14:20.355
And they are progressing fast.

14:20.596 --> 14:23.222
You have to see now in the West,

14:23.222 --> 14:26.608
how are we going to progress

14:26.608 --> 14:29.074
and how are we going to settle down?

14:29.221 --> 14:31.874
It takes time in the West, no doubt to settle down.

14:32.227 --> 14:34.319
Though Realization is much quicker.

14:34.319 --> 14:39.967
Indians get, as I always say that they are difficult nuts to be cracked.

14:40.395 --> 14:44.737
Even British are like that compared to other Europeans.

14:44.918 --> 14:48.039
But those who get Realization also go down very fast, sometimes.

14:48.039 --> 14:50.854
But British, once they get it, they get it all right in their nuts.

14:51.184 --> 14:58.797
They are good. There’s something about their tradition maybe.

14:59.134 --> 15:02.311
But still don’t take too much time to get your Realization.

15:02.647 --> 15:05.838
Why should you get too much time to get your Realization?

15:06.175 --> 15:08.170
You just desire it, it should work.

15:08.170 --> 15:13.435
It’s only your desire that is going to awaken it.

15:13.954 --> 15:17.449
Desire it from your heart, not outwardly.

15:17.449 --> 15:20.014
It’s a fashion nowadays to be a seeker.

15:20.014 --> 15:21.967
No! It is an urge!

15:21.967 --> 15:25.881
You cannot live without it. You have to find it out.

15:25.881 --> 15:28.786
You try anything else.

15:29.368 --> 15:37.045
People are committing suicide because they have not been able to find out their own meanings.

15:37.426 --> 15:42.671
And that’s why it is very important that you must take Sahaja Yoga,

15:42.671 --> 15:49.162
not just like a shopping centre, as like guru shopping, but very seriously

15:49.520 --> 15:57.083
because your meaning is there to be found out.

15:57.083 --> 16:02.411
But your purpose and then the manifestation of your purpose,

16:02.723 --> 16:05.267
that has to happen.

16:05.719 --> 16:09.666
Sahaja Yoga started working in three phases,

16:10.261 --> 16:12.531
in the West I think.

16:12.668 --> 16:16.945
First, that people got their Realization

16:17.500 --> 16:20.452
to see that there’s wrong with them,

16:20.452 --> 16:23.506
where they have got something wrong.

16:23.817 --> 16:29.318
The attention was taken inside by which they could see that they have problems.

16:29.654 --> 16:32.885
If you do not see your problems and somebody says that you have problems,

16:32.885 --> 16:36.250
you’ll hit that person, very badly.

16:36.250 --> 16:39.801
It’s better that you see for yourself that there is a problem.

16:40.219 --> 16:42.650
Once you see that problem within yourself

16:42.805 --> 16:48.056
you will be anxious to see that you get rid of it.

16:48.298 --> 16:51.775
But if you do not see a problem you think that you are doing very great jobs

16:51.775 --> 16:56.230
and you are very great and you are perfectly all right.

16:56.772 --> 17:01.738
Or else, if you see also some of the defects because some people write tha, "This is wrong, that is wrong"

17:01.738 --> 17:05.236
then you become guilty.

17:05.447 --> 17:08.522
Both ways is wrong because one way you go towards ego,

17:08.522 --> 17:12.715
the other way you go towards superego.

17:13.424 --> 17:18.805
So through awakening you start seeing yourself

17:18.805 --> 17:21.221
which side you lie?

17:21.429 --> 17:23.456
What’s the problem?

17:23.456 --> 17:27.391
You start judging yourself. The first judgment starts by yourself.

17:27.529 --> 17:30.488
"Mr. so and so, judge yourself.

17:30.617 --> 17:33.342
Here you are the mirror, now see:

17:33.342 --> 17:35.024
this is what it is".

17:35.024 --> 17:38.275
So you judge yourself and you want to get
rid of it!

17:38.404 --> 17:42.290
You don’t want it anymore within you.

17:42.447 --> 17:45.771
Then the second trouble starts when you start judging others.

17:46.800 --> 17:50.179
First you judge others, you get frightened, “Oh God!

17:50.179 --> 17:54.471
Horrible vibrations, run away. We’ll get caught up!”

17:55.663 --> 17:58.418
Gradually you get immuned.

17:58.418 --> 18:01.963
“Ha! We’ve known this type, we’ve known that type, we’ve known that type,

18:01.963 --> 18:05.667
all these types we know.”

18:06.133 --> 18:09.279
Then you do not condemn anyone but you love

18:09.279 --> 18:14.405
and in that love you judge it.

18:14.742 --> 18:18.650
Because you want others to get rid of their problems,

18:18.650 --> 18:24.739
you help, you share their problems to begin with.

18:25.029 --> 18:33.862
And the joy of giving Realization starts working in you, to others.

18:34.405 --> 18:37.973
Now the problem starts when you look around,

18:37.973 --> 18:40.278
Western society I am talking about.

18:40.278 --> 18:45.357
You find your society is in doldrums.

18:45.678 --> 18:48.533
What’s the problem?

18:48.766 --> 18:51.070
Why the society is in the doldrums? What has happenned?

18:51.070 --> 18:52.708
What basics have we lost?

18:52.708 --> 18:58.041
What part of the sustenance of human beings is lost? Why? Why?

18:58.268 --> 19:03.067
So you find about your marriage institutions,

19:03.171 --> 19:07.861
about your relationship with each other.

19:08.327 --> 19:13.746
That has to be settled. That has to give you joy, real joy of companionship

19:13.746 --> 19:15.270
and love.

19:15.270 --> 19:20.807
And in the third phase, the great who are trying to be born on this Earth,

19:20.962 --> 19:24.693
so many of them. They are around here.

19:24.901 --> 19:29.669
Just here, watching. They have to be born.

19:29.850 --> 19:34.139
You have to be parents of those children.

19:34.528 --> 19:39.319
They are going to blast all these satanic forces

19:39.320 --> 19:42.024
because they know what these satans are like

19:42.024 --> 19:43.845
and how they are to be blasted.

19:43.845 --> 19:48.731
They are experts. I have seen so many of them and you have seen also.

19:48.861 --> 19:51.561
They know what is Kundalini. They know how to raise it

19:51.561 --> 19:57.656
and they know how to blast all these people.

19:57.763 --> 20:08.027
And then, the whole society of Realized souls

20:08.027 --> 20:12.394
is going to pull out this humanity.

20:12.394 --> 20:17.326
Every one need not be brought to Sahaja Yoga; they’ll be all pulled out.

20:17.326 --> 20:23.158
We must have sufficient pulling force within us.

20:23.380 --> 20:27.994
So those who come to Me earlier have a greater responsibility

20:28.198 --> 20:31.637
than those who’ll be coming much later say, after ten years.

20:31.637 --> 20:34.887
They’ll be just jumping into it.

20:34.887 --> 20:38.723
You are the ones who are going to do that.

20:38.873 --> 20:42.738
So, judge your self-esteem

20:43.229 --> 20:49.384
and do not try to condemn yourself for anything.
That’s forbidden in Sahaja Yoga, you know that.

20:49.650 --> 20:54.371
You are all saints. So many saints sitting here imagine!

20:54.966 --> 20:58.838
The gods are singing.

20:59.110 --> 21:09.162
The angels are showering all their joy upon you.

21:09.618 --> 21:12.709
What a meeting it is!

21:12.709 --> 21:18.373
What a force it is!

21:19.560 --> 21:26.063
The auspiciousness of this meeting acts not only in England,

21:26.063 --> 21:33.053
not only in Europe, but in the whole universe.

21:33.326 --> 21:37.154
But the channels have to be strong enough to manifest it.

21:37.672 --> 21:46.261
That’s why today I said, “I have to say something really serious”.

21:47.595 --> 21:53.243
On the 27th, we are going to have a big puja, you know that

21:53.736 --> 21:58.849
and I would like you to think about what I have said today.

21:59.134 --> 22:06.708
And I would like you also to proclaim within yourself that

22:06.864 --> 22:12.202
you will establish this Mahayoga on this Earth.

22:12.377 --> 22:16.588
That you will bring

22:16.769 --> 22:21.701
the blessings of this golden age on this Earth,

22:21.701 --> 22:23.668
which was created for this.

22:23.668 --> 22:26.856
The whole creation will find its own meaning.

22:27.051 --> 22:29.633
May God bless you.

22:36.742 --> 22:41.495
I would request you to put your hands like
this towards Me - just like that.

22:41.696 --> 22:43.880
Then the vibrations are so strong.

22:44.081 --> 22:49.340
Like this there is not going to be any
difficulty in receiving realization.

22:49.541 --> 22:56.481
Close your eyes. Put your feet straight on
the ground as far as possible. It's better.
